hopobject.body: Have you read any good books lately? healthyminerals.com This logical choice of language reinforces the fact that what has been witnessed is an institutional or systemic failure, largely self-induced, through which the banks in effect introduced a cancer into the wider economy and as a result the whole developed world has endured a form of collective chemotherapy, from which we are only now emerging. Some substantial change in the British and European regulatory regime was inevitable and welcome.
